Please disable browser caching for proper plot display.

Click "Hero Search", then enter the full name of a dota2 hero for hero details.

Click "Pro Teams", to see the name of some professonal teams of different regions.
Click on a team name to see the player name aviliable in the system.
Click on a player's name to see his/her up to 10 recent match infomation.

Click on "Player Search", then enter the user name of a dota2 player. 
Infomation of up to 10 recent matches of the closest matched player will be displayed